<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">谢邀。<br>那些束缚、挣扎、纠缠，超越了宗教、种族、年龄。<br>而我已经分不清，这火花是不是来自爱情，却已被它熏灼出火眼金睛。<br><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/863e1c9ff16329138d73e04b4dac485b_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="460" data-rawheight="524" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="460" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/863e1c9ff16329138d73e04b4dac485b_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="460" data-rawheight="524" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="460" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/863e1c9ff16329138d73e04b4dac485b_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/863e1c9ff16329138d73e04b4dac485b_b.jpg">


